  }, {
    "tStartMs": 277644,
    "dDurationMs": 1635,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and the power of your voice.\"\nAnd so I just..."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 279279,
    "dDurationMs": 1902,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "I went to my happy place.\nI did my best."
