  }, {
    "tStartMs": 287654,
    "dDurationMs": 1735,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which is from a place in Italy."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 289389,
    "dDurationMs": 1268,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Don't ask me where.\nI've done some research,"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 290657,
    "dDurationMs": 1902,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "not all of it.\n-Okay. Yeah, yeah, of course."
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 292559,
    "dDurationMs": 1769,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "-But the idea is,\nbefore you get married --"
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 294328,
    "dDurationMs": 1501,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "There's a false-marriage story\nin this."
